“Once the clean record is created, I layer in three types of data quality issues.

_inject_nulls randomly introduces missing values across non‑critical fields, simulating upstream API gaps or incomplete ETL loads.

_inject_invalid_values injects domain‑aware violations — negative prices, negative quantities, future timestamps, and invalid order statuses — which are the kinds of issues that pass schema validation but break business rules.”

